ButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pvd1665703273990.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvd1665703273990.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvd1665703273990.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pvd1665703273990\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n /show\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pvd1665703273990___show_488485\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Show the parameters used by the specified Uniface Router service on Microsoft Windows.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__topic_d150935e1_d150936e1_d150937e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__p_d150938e1_d150939e1_d150940e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/show</span>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">=\"</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServiceName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__topic_d108742e1_d108743e1_d108744e1_d108745e1_d108746e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184837e71\">\n                  \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__p_d150944e1_d150945e1_d150946e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServiceName</var>—name of a Uniface Router service previously installed using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inst</span> switch. If you do not specify the <var class=\"keyword varname\">ServiceName</var>, the default name <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface<var class=\"keyword varname\">Version</var> URouter</code> is assumed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__topic_d108747e1_d108748e1_d108749e1_d108750e1_d108751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184837e95\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__d6009e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter</span>—Uniface Router on Microsoft Windows. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hjn1665702738471.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjn1665702738471.html\" title=\"Executable file for the Uniface Router.\">urouter</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__topic_d108752e1_d108753e1_d108754e1_d108755e1_d108756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1184837e114\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__p_d150956e1_d150957e1_d150958e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/show</span> switch is used only on the command line with <code class=\"ph codeph\">urouter.exe</code> to display the parameters with which a Uniface Router service was installed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__p_d150959e1_d150960e1_d150961e1\">It is useful for determining errors in unsuccessful attempts to install the Uniface Router.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__fig_wyt_ylb_ddc\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Specified <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter</span> successfully installed</figcaption>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre screen language-plaintext\" id=\"pvd1665703273990__pre_hx2_1mb_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">D:/Uniface/Uniface10/common/bin&gt;urouter /show=\"uniface 10 urouter 2\"\nService 'uniface 10 urouter 2' was installed without parameters.</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</figure>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cle1665702738757.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/inst</a><p>Install and register the Uniface Router as a Windows service under a unique service name.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531095\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531095\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/show Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /show Show the parameters used by the specified Uniface Router service on Microsoft Windows. /show { =\" ServiceName \" } Arguments ServiceName —name of a Uniface Router service previously installed using the /inst switch. If you do not specify the ServiceName , the default name Uniface Version URouter is assumed. Use With urouter —Uniface Router on Microsoft Windows. For more information, see urouter . Description The /show switch is used only on the command line with urouter.exe to display the parameters with which a Uniface Router service was installed. It is useful for determining errors in unsuccessful attempts to install the Uniface Router. Figure 1. Specified urouter successfully installed D:/Uniface/Uniface10/common/bin>urouter /show=\"uniface 10 urouter 2\" Service 'uniface 10 urouter 2' was installed without parameters. Copy Related Links /inst Install and register the Uniface Router as a Windows service under a unique service name. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}